@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v1
    v2 = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.63 / v0 + 0.52)) * (wp.exp(v1 + 0.00) - 0.15))
    tmp = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.29 - v1 + 0.67)) / ((v1 + 0.43 + v2 + 0.05) / (v1 + 0.74 + v2 + 0.68)))
    v0 = wp.cos((v0 - (v0 + 0.80 / tmp + 0.92)))
    tmp = (tmp * ((v0 + 0.28 / v1 + 0.57) * v1))
    v0 = v2
    tmp = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.47 / tmp + 0.61)) - wp.abs(wp.exp(v2 + 0.69)))
    data[tid] = v0
